Date: January 30th 2024

Summary: LEVEL 0.1 THE DANGER ZONE: Player getting stuck on the door

Priority or Severity: A

Visibility: High

Type: Collision

Reproduction Rate: 70%

Description: When the player opens the door and right away walks through it, there is a chance the player will no-clip inside the door hinge and get stuck, unable to move

Launch Title
Make your way through the game until you reach Level 0.1
Head to the underground of the level
Open a door and walk through at the same time

Result: High chance that the player will clip into the doorframe, causing them immobile

Expected Results: Player is able to open the door and walk through

